{"title":"Katherine N Thompson, PhD","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Katherine N Thompson, PhD","format":"html","editor":"visual"},"headingText":"About me","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n\nHello!\n\nI am postdoctoral researcher in psychiatric epidemiology who conducts quantitative research on depression, social isolation, and health equity. I am based in the Department of Sociology at Purdue University with a PhD in Social, Genetic, and Developmental Psychology from King’s College London. \n\nI committed to open, diverse, and communicable science. \n\n![](images/headshot.jpeg){fig-align=\"center\" width=\"300px\"}\n\n## Connect\n\n[GitHub](https://github.com/knthompson26)\n\n[Google Scholar](https://scholar.google.co.uk/citations?hl=en&user=xD4dn1IAAAAJ)\n\n[LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/katherine-thompson-79a60b390/)\n\n[Bluesky](https://bsky.app/profile/ktnthompson.bsky.social)\n\n[ORCID](https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1818-0428)\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n## About me\n\nHello!\n\nI am postdoctoral researcher in psychiatric epidemiology who conducts quantitative research on depression, social isolation, and health equity. I am based in the Department of Sociology at Purdue University with a PhD in Social, Genetic, and Developmental Psychology from King’s College London. \n\nI committed to open, diverse, and communicable science. \n\n![](images/headshot.jpeg){fig-align=\"center\" width=\"300px\"}\n\n## Connect\n\n[GitHub](https://github.com/knthompson26)\n\n[Google Scholar](https://scholar.google.co.uk/citations?hl=en&user=xD4dn1IAAAAJ)\n\n[LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/katherine-thompson-79a60b390/)\n\n[Bluesky](https://bsky.app/profile/ktnthompson.bsky.social)\n\n[ORCID](https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1818-0428)\n"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"f